#### @FeignClient(fallbackFactory=…)
> 支持打印出异常日志（推荐）

```
package com.mumu.springcloud_feign.service;

import org.springframework.cloud.openfeign.FallbackFactory;
import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;

@Component
public class SchedualServiceHiHystricFacotry implements FallbackFactory<SchedualServiceHi> {

    @Override
    public SchedualServiceHi create(Throwable cause) {
        return new SchedualServiceHi() {
            @Override
            public String sayHiFromClientOne(String name) {
                System.out.println("异常日志error:"+cause);
                return "FallbackFactory | sorry! 网络异常，服务暂时无法访问。 请求的name为:"+name;
            }
        };
    }
}

```

